\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Rerouted-query MRR across $\alpha \in [0.3, 1.0]$ on validation (left) and test (right). Dashed line is the mFAR baseline. All three configurations peak near $\alpha \approx 0.7$ on test and $\alpha \approx 0.5$ on val; Memory v2 (red) is the upper envelope across the full range.}}{7}}
